headline: Eli Lilly Just Made Another Move to Dominate the Weight Loss Market: Should You Buy the Stock?
summary: Eli Lilly made a move that could help address a drawback of its anti-obesity medicines.  Lilly's business extends far beyond this highly lucrative market.  Eli Lilly (NYSE: LLY) is one of the undisputed leaders in the fast-growing market for weight-management medicines.
